Name: Avatar
Text ShortCut: A paraplegic Marine dispatched to the moon Pandora on a unique mission becomes torn between following his orders and protecting the world he feels is his home.

Name: Avengers: Endgame
Text ShortCut: After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War, the universe is in ruins. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers assemble once more in order to reverse Thanos' actions and restore balance to the universe.

Name: Titanic
Text ShortCut: A seventeen-year-old aristocrat falls in love with a kind but poor artist aboard the luxurious, ill-fated R.M.S. Titanic.

Name: Star Wars: Episode VII - The Force Awakens
Text ShortCut: As a new threat to the galaxy rises, Rey, a desert scavenger, and Finn, an ex-stormtrooper, must join Han Solo and Chewbacca to search for the one hope of restoring peace.

Name: Avengers: Infinity War
Text ShortCut: The Avengers and their allies must be willing to sacrifice all in an attempt to defeat the powerful Thanos before his blitz of devastation and ruin puts an end to the universe.

Name: Spider-Man: No Way Home
Text ShortCut: With Spider-Man's identity now revealed, Peter asks Doctor Strange for help. When a spell goes wrong, dangerous foes from other worlds start to appear, forcing Peter to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.

Name: Jurassic World
Text ShortCut: A new theme park, built on the original site of Jurassic Park, creates a genetically modified hybrid dinosaur, the Indominus Rex, which escapes containment and goes on a killing spree.

Name: The Lion King
Text ShortCut: After the murder of his father, a young lion prince flees his kingdom only to learn the true meaning of responsibility and bravery.

Name: The Avengers
Text ShortCut: Earth's mightiest heroes must come together and learn to fight as a team if they are going to stop the mischievous Loki and his alien army from enslaving humanity.

Name: Furious 7
Text ShortCut: Deckard Shaw seeks revenge against Dominic Toretto and his family for his comatose brother.

Name: Frozen II
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Musical
Text ShortCut: Anna, Elsa, Kristoff, Olaf and Sven leave Arendelle to travel to an ancient, autumn-bound forest of an enchanted land. They set out to find the origin of Elsa's powers in order to save their kingdom.

Name: Avengers: Age of Ultron
Text ShortCut: When Tony Stark and Bruce Banner try to jump-start a dormant peacekeeping program called Ultron, things go horribly wrong and it's up to Earth's mightiest heroes to stop the villainous Ultron from enacting his terrible plan.

Name: Black Panther
Text ShortCut: T'Challa, heir to the hidden but advanced kingdom of Wakanda, must step forward to lead his people into a new future and must confront a challenger from his country's past.

Name: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2
Text ShortCut: Harry, Ron, and Hermione search for Voldemort's remaining Horcruxes in their effort to destroy the Dark Lord as the final battle rages on at Hogwarts.

Name: Star Wars: Episode VIII - The Last Jedi
Text ShortCut: The Star Wars saga continues as new heroes and galactic legends go on an epic adventure, unlocking mysteries of the Force and shocking revelations of the past.

Name: Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom
Text ShortCut: When the island's dormant volcano begins roaring to life, Owen and Claire mount a campaign to rescue the remaining dinosaurs from this extinction-level event.

Name: Frozen
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Musical
Text ShortCut: When the newly crowned Queen Elsa accidentally uses her power to turn things into ice to curse her home in infinite winter, her sister Anna teams up with a mountain man, his playful reindeer, and a snowman to change the weather condition.

Name: Beauty and the Beast
Text ShortCut: A selfish Prince is cursed to become a monster for the rest of his life, unless he learns to fall in love with a beautiful young woman he keeps prisoner.

Name: Incredibles 2
Generes: Action, Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: The Incredibles family takes on a new mission which involves a change in family roles: Bob Parr (Mr. Incredible) must manage the house while his wife Helen (Elastigirl) goes out to save the world.

Name: The Fate of the Furious
Text ShortCut: When a mysterious woman seduces Dominic Toretto into the world of terrorism and a betrayal of those closest to him, the crew face trials that will test them as never before.

Name: Iron Man 3
Text ShortCut: When Tony Stark's world is torn apart by a formidable terrorist called the Mandarin, he starts an odyssey of rebuilding and retribution.

Name: Minions
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Crime, Family, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: Minions Stuart, Kevin, and Bob are recruited by Scarlet Overkill, a supervillain who, alongside her inventor husband Herb, hatches a plot to take over the world.

Name: Captain America: Civil War
Text ShortCut: Political involvement in the Avengers' affairs causes a rift between Captain America and Iron Man.

Name: Aquaman
Text ShortCut: Arthur Curry, the human-born heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, goes on a quest to prevent a war between the worlds of ocean and land.

Name: The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King
Text ShortCut: Gandalf and Aragorn lead the World of Men against Sauron's army to draw his gaze from Frodo and Sam as they approach Mount Doom with the One Ring.

Name: Spider-Man: Far from Home
Text ShortCut: Following the events of Avengers: Endgame, Spider-Man must step up to take on new threats in a world that has changed forever.

Name: Captain Marvel
Text ShortCut: Carol Danvers becomes one of the universe's most powerful heroes when Earth is caught in the middle of a galactic war between two alien races.

Name: Transformers: Dark of the Moon
Text ShortCut: The Autobots learn of a Cybertronian spacecraft hidden on the moon, and race against the Decepticons to reach it and to learn its secrets.

Name: Skyfall
Text ShortCut: James Bond's loyalty to M is tested when her past comes back to haunt her. When MI6 comes under attack, 007 must track down and destroy the threat, no matter how personal the cost.

Name: Transformers: Age of Extinction
Text ShortCut: When humanity allies with a bounty hunter in pursuit of Optimus Prime, the Autobots turn to a mechanic and his family for help.

Name: Jurassic Park
Text ShortCut: A pragmatic paleontologist touring an almost complete theme park on an island in Central America is tasked with protecting a couple of kids after a power failure causes the park's cloned dinosaurs to run loose.

Name: The Dark Knight Rises
Text ShortCut: Eight years after the Joker's reign of anarchy, Batman, with the help of the enigmatic Catwoman, is forced from his exile to save Gotham City from the brutal guerrilla terrorist Bane.

Name: Joker
Text ShortCut: A mentally troubled stand-up comedian embarks on a downward spiral that leads to the creation of an iconic villain.

Name: Star Wars: Episode IX - The Rise of Skywalker
Text ShortCut: In the riveting conclusion of the landmark Skywalker saga, new legends will be born-and the final battle for freedom is yet to come.

Name: Toy Story 4
Text ShortCut: When a new toy called "Forky" joins Woody and the gang, a road trip alongside old and new friends reveals how big the world can be for a toy.

Name: Toy Story 3
Text ShortCut: The toys are mistakenly delivered to a day-care center instead of the attic right before Andy leaves for college, and it's up to Woody to convince the other toys that they weren't abandoned and to return home.

Name: Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest
Text ShortCut: Jack Sparrow races to recover the heart of Davy Jones to avoid enslaving his soul to Jones' service, as other friends and foes seek the heart for their own agenda as well.

Name: The Lion King
Text ShortCut: Lion prince Simba and his father are targeted by his bitter uncle, who wants to ascend the throne himself.

Name: Rogue One: A Star Wars Story
Text ShortCut: In a time of conflict, a group of unlikely heroes band together on a mission to steal the plans to the Death Star, the Empire's ultimate weapon of destruction.

Name: Aladdin
Generes: Adventure, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Musical, Romance
Text ShortCut: A kind-hearted street urchin and a power-hungry Grand Vizier vie for a magic lamp that has the power to make their deepest wishes come true.

Name: Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides
Text ShortCut: Jack Sparrow and Barbossa embark on a quest to find the elusive fountain of youth, only to discover that Blackbeard and his daughter are after it too.

Name: Despicable Me 3
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Crime, Family, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: Gru meets his long-lost, charming, cheerful, and more successful twin brother Dru, who wants to team up with him for one last criminal heist.

Name: Finding Dory
Text ShortCut: Friendly but forgetful blue tang Dory begins a search for her long-lost parents, and everyone learns a few things about the real meaning of family along the way.

Name: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
Text ShortCut: Two Jedi escape a hostile blockade to find allies and come across a young boy who may bring balance to the Force, but the long dormant Sith resurface to claim their original glory.

Name: Alice in Wonderland
Text ShortCut: Nineteen-year-old Alice returns to the magical world from her childhood adventure, where she reunites with her old friends and learns of her true destiny: to end the Red Queen's reign of terror.

Name: Zootopia
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Crime, Family, Mystery
Text ShortCut: In a city of anthropomorphic animals, a rookie bunny cop and a cynical con artist fox must work together to uncover a conspiracy.

Name: Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone
Text ShortCut: An orphaned boy enrolls in a school of wizardry, where he learns the truth about himself, his family and the terrible evil that haunts the magical world.

Name: The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey
Text ShortCut: A reluctant Hobbit, Bilbo Baggins, sets out to the Lonely Mountain with a spirited group of dwarves to reclaim their mountain home, and the gold within it from the dragon Smaug.

Name: The Dark Knight
Text ShortCut: When the menace known as the Joker wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.

Name: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 1
Text ShortCut: As Harry, Ron, and Hermione race against time and evil to destroy the Horcruxes, they uncover the existence of the three most powerful objects in the wizarding world: the Deathly Hallows.

Name: Despicable Me 2
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Crime, Family, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: When Gru, the world's most super-bad turned super-dad has been recruited by a team of officials to stop lethal muscle and a host of Gru's own, He has to fight back with new gadgetry, cars, and more minion madness.

Name: The Jungle Book
Text ShortCut: After a threat from the tiger Shere Khan forces him to flee the jungle, a man-cub named Mowgli embarks on a journey of self discovery with the help of panther Bagheera and free-spirited bear Baloo.

Name: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
Text ShortCut: Four teenagers are sucked into a magical video game, and the only way they can escape is to work together to finish the game.

Name: The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies
Text ShortCut: Bilbo and company are forced to engage in a war against an array of combatants and keep the Lonely Mountain from falling into the hands of a rising darkness.

Name: Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End
Text ShortCut: Captain Barbossa, Will Turner and Elizabeth Swann must sail off the edge of the map, navigate treachery and betrayal, find Jack Sparrow, and make their final alliances for one last decisive battle.

Name: The Hobbit: The Desolation of Smaug
Text ShortCut: The dwarves, along with Bilbo Baggins and Gandalf the Grey, continue their quest to reclaim Erebor, their homeland, from Smaug. Bilbo Baggins is in possession of a mysterious and magical ring.

Name: The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers
Text ShortCut: While Frodo and Sam edge closer to Mordor with the help of the shifty Gollum, the divided fellowship makes a stand against Sauron's new ally, Saruman, and his hordes of Isengard.

Name: Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix
Text ShortCut: With their warning about Lord Voldemort's return scoffed at, Harry and Dumbledore are targeted by the Wizard authorities as an authoritarian bureaucrat slowly seizes power at Hogwarts.

Name: Finding Nemo
Text ShortCut: After his son is captured in the Great Barrier Reef and taken to Sydney, a timid clownfish sets out on a journey to bring him home.

Name: Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince
Text ShortCut: As Harry Potter begins his sixth year at Hogwarts, he discovers an old book marked as "the property of the Half-Blood Prince" and begins to learn more about Lord Voldemort's dark past.

Name: Shrek 2
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Romance
Text ShortCut: Shrek and Fiona travel to the Kingdom of Far Far Away, where Fiona's parents are King and Queen, to celebrate their marriage. When they arrive, they find they are not as welcome as they thought they would be.

Name: Bohemian Rhapsody
Text ShortCut: The story of the legendary British rock band Queen and lead singer Freddie Mercury, leading up to their famous performance at Live Aid.

Name: The Battle at Lake Changjin
Text ShortCut: Set in the Second Phase Offensive of the Korean War, "The Battle at Lake Changjin" tells an epic historical tale: 71 years ago, the People's Volunteer Army (PVA) entered North Korea for battle. Under extreme freezing conditions, the troops on the Eastern Front pursued with fearless spirit and iron will, as they courageously fought the enemy at Lake Changjin (also known as Chosin Reservoir). The battle was a turning point in the Korean War and demonstrated the courage and resolve of the PVA.

Name: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring
Text ShortCut: A meek Hobbit from the Shire and eight companions set out on a journey to destroy the powerful One Ring and save Middle-earth from the Dark Lord Sauron.

Name: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire
Text ShortCut: Harry Potter finds himself competing in a hazardous tournament between rival schools of magic, but he is distracted by recurring nightmares.

Name: Spider-Man 3
Text ShortCut: A strange black entity from another world bonds with Peter Parker and causes inner turmoil as he contends with new villains, temptations, and revenge.

Name: Ice Age 3: Dawn of the Dinosaurs
Text ShortCut: When Sid's attempt to adopt three dinosaur eggs gets him abducted by their real mother to an underground lost world, his friends attempt to rescue him.

Name: Spectre
Text ShortCut: A cryptic message from James Bond's past sends him on a trail to uncover the existence of a sinister organisation named SPECTRE. With a new threat dawning, Bond learns the terrible truth about the author of all his pain in his most recent missions.

Name: Spider-Man: Homecoming
Text ShortCut: Peter Parker balances his life as an ordinary high school student in Queens with his superhero alter-ego Spider-Man, and finds himself on the trail of a new menace prowling the skies of New York City.

Name: Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets
Text ShortCut: An ancient prophecy seems to be coming true when a mysterious presence begins stalking the corridors of a school of magic and leaving its victims paralyzed.

Name: Ice Age 4: Continental Drift
Text ShortCut: Manny, Diego, and Sid embark upon another adventure after their continent is set adrift. Using an iceberg as a ship, they encounter sea creatures and battle pirates as they explore a new world.

Name: The Secret Life of Pets
Text ShortCut: The quiet life of a terrier named Max is upended when his owner takes in Duke, a stray whom Max instantly dislikes.

Name: Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice
Text ShortCut: Fearing that the actions of Superman are left unchecked, Batman takes on the Man of Steel, while the world wrestles with what kind of a hero it really needs.

Name: Wolf Warrior 2
Text ShortCut: China's deadliest special forces operative settles into a quiet life on the sea. When sadistic mercenaries begin targeting nearby civilians, he must leave his newfound peace behind and return to his duties as a soldier and protector.

Name: Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith
Text ShortCut: Three years into the Clone Wars, the Jedi rescue Palpatine from Count Dooku. As Obi-Wan pursues a new threat, Anakin acts as a double agent between the Jedi Council and Palpatine and is lured into a sinister plan to rule the galaxy.

Name: The Hunger Games: Catching Fire
Text ShortCut: Katniss Everdeen and Peeta Mellark become targets of the Capitol after their victory in the 74th Hunger Games sparks a rebellion in the Districts of Panem.

Name: Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2
Text ShortCut: The Guardians struggle to keep together as a team while dealing with their personal family issues, notably Star-Lord's encounter with his father the ambitious celestial being Ego.

Name: Inside Out
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Drama, Family, Fantasy
Text ShortCut: After young Riley is uprooted from her Midwest life and moved to San Francisco, her emotions - Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness - conflict on how best to navigate a new city, house, and school.

Name: Venom
Text ShortCut: A failed reporter is bonded to an alien entity, one of many symbiotes who have invaded Earth. But the being takes a liking to Earth and decides to protect it.

Name: Thor: Ragnarok
Text ShortCut: Imprisoned on the planet Sakaar, Thor must race against time to return to Asgard and stop Ragnarök, the destruction of his world, at the hands of the powerful and ruthless villain Hela.

Name: Inception
Text ShortCut: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O., but his tragic past may doom the project and his team to disaster.

Name: Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen
Text ShortCut: Sam Witwicky leaves the Autobots behind for a normal life. But when his mind is filled with cryptic symbols, the Decepticons target him and he is dragged back into the Transformers' war.

Name: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 2
Text ShortCut: After the birth of Renesmee/Nessie, the Cullens gather other vampire clans in order to protect the child from a false allegation that puts the family in front of the Volturi.

Name: Spider-Man
Text ShortCut: When bitten by a genetically modified spider, a nerdy, shy, and awkward high school student gains spider-like abilities that he eventually must use to fight evil as a superhero after tragedy befalls his family.

Name: Wonder Woman
Text ShortCut: When a pilot crashes and tells of conflict in the outside world, Diana, an Amazonian warrior in training, leaves home to fight a war, discovering her full powers and true destiny.

Name: Hi, Mom
Text ShortCut: A woman travels back in time to befriend her own mother in an attempt to make her life better.

Name: Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness
Text ShortCut: Doctor Strange teams up with a mysterious teenage girl from his dreams who can travel across multiverses, to battle multiple threats, including other-universe versions of himself, which threaten to wipe out millions across the multiverse. They seek help from Wanda the Scarlet Witch, Wong and others.

Name: Independence Day
Text ShortCut: The aliens are coming and their goal is to invade and destroy Earth. Fighting superior technology, mankind's best weapon is the will to survive.

Name: Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them
Text ShortCut: The adventures of writer Newt Scamander in New York's secret community of witches and wizards seventy years before Harry Potter reads his book in school.

Name: Shrek the Third
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Romance
Text ShortCut: Reluctantly designated as the heir to the land of Far, Far Away, Shrek hatches a plan to install the rebellious Artie as the new king while Princess Fiona tries to fend off a coup d'état by the jilted Prince Charming.

Name: Coco
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Music, Mystery
Text ShortCut: Aspiring musician Miguel, confronted with his family's ancestral ban on music, enters the Land of the Dead to find his great-great-grandfather, a legendary singer.

Name: Jumanji: The Next Level
Text ShortCut: In Jumanji: The Next Level, the gang is back but the game has changed. As they return to rescue one of their own, the players will have to brave parts unknown from arid deserts to snowy mountains, to escape the world's most dangerous game.

Name: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban
Text ShortCut: Harry Potter, Ron and Hermione return to Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry for their third year of study, where they delve into the mystery surrounding an escaped prisoner who poses a dangerous threat to the young wizard.

Name: Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales
Text ShortCut: Captain Jack Sparrow is pursued by old rival Captain Salazar and a crew of deadly ghosts who have escaped from the Devil's Triangle. They're determined to kill every pirate at sea...notably Jack.

Name: E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial
Text ShortCut: A troubled child summons the courage to help a friendly alien escape from Earth and return to his home planet.

Name: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
Text ShortCut: Ethan Hunt and his IMF team, along with some familiar allies, race against time after a mission gone wrong.
A frustrated writer struggles to keep his family alive when a series of global catastrophes threatens to annihilate mankind.

Name: Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull
Text ShortCut: In 1957, archaeologist and adventurer Dr. Henry "Indiana" Jones, Jr. is called back into action and becomes entangled in a Soviet plot to uncover the secret behind mysterious artifacts known as the Crystal Skulls.

Name: Spider-Man 2
Text ShortCut: Peter Parker is beset with troubles in his failing personal life as he battles a brilliant scientist named Doctor Otto Octavius.

Name: Fast & Furious 6
Text ShortCut: Hobbs has Dominic and Brian reassemble their crew to take down a team of mercenaries: Dominic unexpectedly gets sidetracked with facing his presumed deceased girlfriend, Letty.

Name: Deadpool 2
Text ShortCut: Foul-mouthed mutant mercenary Wade Wilson (a.k.a. Deadpool) assembles a team of fellow mutant rogues to protect a young boy with supernatural abilities from the brutal, time-traveling cyborg Cable.

Name: Deadpool
Text ShortCut: A wisecracking mercenary gets experimented on and becomes immortal but ugly, and sets out to track down the man who ruined his looks.

Name: Star Wars
Text ShortCut: Luke Skywalker joins forces with a Jedi Knight, a cocky pilot, a Wookiee and two droids to save the galaxy from the Empire's world-destroying battle station, while also attempting to rescue Princess Leia from the mysterious Darth Vader.

Name: No Time to Die
Text ShortCut: James Bond has left active service. His peace is short-lived when Felix Leiter, an old friend from the CIA, turns up asking for help, leading Bond onto the trail of a mysterious villain armed with dangerous new technology.

Name: Guardians of the Galaxy
Text ShortCut: A group of intergalactic criminals must pull together to stop a fanatical warrior with plans to purge the universe.

Name: The Batman
Text ShortCut: When a sadistic serial killer begins murdering key political figures in Gotham, Batman is forced to investigate the city's hidden corruption and question his family's involvement.

Name: The Da Vinci Code
Text ShortCut: A murder inside the Louvre, and clues in Da Vinci paintings, lead to the discovery of a religious mystery protected by a secret society for two thousand years, which could shake the foundations of Christianity.

Name: Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw
Text ShortCut: Lawman Luke Hobbs (Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson) and outcast Deckard Shaw (Jason Statham) form an unlikely alliance when a cyber-genetically enhanced villain threatens the future of humanity.

Name: Maleficent
Text ShortCut: A vengeful fairy is driven to curse an infant princess, only to discover that the child may be the one person who can restore peace to their troubled land.

Name: The Amazing Spider-Man
Text ShortCut: After Peter Parker is bitten by a genetically altered spider, he gains newfound, spider-like powers and ventures out to save the city from the machinations of a mysterious reptilian foe.

Name: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 1
Text ShortCut: Katniss Everdeen is in District 13 after she shatters the games forever. Under the leadership of President Coin and the advice of her trusted friends, Katniss spreads her wings as she fights to save Peeta and a nation moved by her courage.

Name: Shrek Forever After
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Romance
Text ShortCut: Rumpelstiltskin tricks a mid-life crisis burdened Shrek into allowing himself to be erased from existence and cast in a dark alternate timeline where Rumpelstiltskin rules supreme.

Name: Madagascar 3: Europe's Most Wanted
Text ShortCut: The Madagascar animals join a struggling European circus to get back to New York, but find themselves being pursued by a psychotic animal control officer.

Name: Suicide Squad
Text ShortCut: A secret government agency recruits some of the most dangerous incarcerated super-villains to form a defensive task force. Their first mission: save the world from the apocalypse.

Name: X-Men: Days of Future Past
Text ShortCut: The X-Men send Wolverine to the past in a desperate effort to change history and prevent an event that results in doom for both humans and mutants.

Name: The Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe
Text ShortCut: Four kids travel through a wardrobe to the land of Narnia and learn of their destiny to free it with the guidance of a mystical lion.

Name: Monsters University
Text ShortCut: A look at the relationship between Mike Wazowski (Billy Crystal) and James P. "Sully" Sullivan (John Goodman) during their days at Monsters University, when they weren't necessarily the best of friends.

Name: The Matrix Reloaded
Text ShortCut: Freedom fighters Neo, Trinity and Morpheus continue to lead the revolt against the Machine Army, unleashing their arsenal of extraordinary skills and weaponry against the systematic forces of repression and exploitation.

Name: Up
Text ShortCut: 78-year-old Carl Fredricksen travels to Paradise Falls in his house equipped with balloons, inadvertently taking a young stowaway.

Name: Ne Zha
Generes: Action, Adventure, Animation, Family, Fantasy, Thriller
Text ShortCut: Born with unique powers, a boy is recruited to fight demons and save the community that fears him.

Name: F9: The Fast Saga
Text ShortCut: Dom and the crew must take on an international terrorist who turns out to be Dom and Mia's estranged brother.

Name: Gravity
Text ShortCut: Two astronauts work together to survive after an accident leaves them stranded in space.

Name: Captain America: The Winter Soldier
Text ShortCut: As Steve Rogers struggles to embrace his role in the modern world, he teams up with a fellow Avenger and S.H.I.E.L.D agent, Black Widow, to battle a new threat from history: an assassin known as the Winter Soldier.

Name: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 1
Text ShortCut: The Quileutes close in on expecting parents Edward and Bella, whose unborn child poses a threat to the Wolf Pack and the towns people of Forks.

Name: The Twilight Saga: New Moon
Text ShortCut: Edward leaves Bella after an attack that nearly claimed her life, and, in her depression, she falls into yet another difficult relationship - this time with her close friend, Jacob Black.

Name: Dawn of the Planet of the Apes
Text ShortCut: A growing nation of genetically evolved apes led by Caesar is threatened by a band of human survivors of the devastating virus unleashed a decade earlier.

Name: Transformers
Text ShortCut: An ancient struggle between two Cybertronian races, the heroic Autobots and the evil Decepticons, comes to Earth, with a clue to the ultimate power held by a teenager.

Name: The Amazing Spider-Man 2
Text ShortCut: When New York is put under siege by Oscorp, it is up to Spider-Man to save the city he swore to protect as well as his loved ones.

Name: It
Text ShortCut: In the summer of 1989, a group of bullied kids band together to destroy a shape-shifting monster, which disguises itself as a clown and preys on the children of Derry, their small Maine town.

Name: Interstellar
Text ShortCut: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

Name: The Wandering Earth
Text ShortCut: As the sun is dying out, people all around the world build giant planet thrusters to move Earth out of its orbit and sail Earth to a new star system. Yet the 2500-year journey comes with unexpected dangers, and in order to save humanity, a group of young people in this age of a wandering Earth fight hard for the survival of humankind.

Name: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
Generes: Action, Adventure, Drama, Fantasy, Romance, Thriller
Text ShortCut: As a string of mysterious killings grips Seattle, Bella, whose high school graduation is fast approaching, is forced to choose between her love for vampire Edward and her friendship with werewolf Jacob.

Name: Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol
Text ShortCut: The IMF is shut down when it's implicated in the bombing of the Kremlin, causing Ethan Hunt and his new team to go rogue to clear their organization's name.

Name: The Hunger Games
Text ShortCut: Katniss Everdeen voluntarily takes her younger sister's place in the Hunger Games: a televised competition in which two teenagers from each of the twelve Districts of Panem are chosen at random to fight to the death.

Name: Detective Chinatown 3
Text ShortCut: A major crime occurs in Tokyo when detectives Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to investigate the crime. A battle between the strongest detectives in Asia is about to break out with bursts of laughter.

Name: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation
Text ShortCut: Ethan and his team take on their most impossible mission yet when they have to eradicate an international rogue organization as highly skilled as they are and committed to destroying the IMF.

Name: Forrest Gump
Text ShortCut: The presidencies of Kennedy and Johnson, the Vietnam War, the Watergate scandal and other historical events unfold from the perspective of an Alabama man with an IQ of 75, whose only desire is to be reunited with his childhood sweetheart.

Name: Doctor Strange
Text ShortCut: While on a journey of physical and spiritual healing, a brilliant neurosurgeon is drawn into the world of the mystic arts.

Name: The Sixth Sense
Text ShortCut: A frightened, withdrawn Philadelphia boy who communicates with spirits seeks the help of a disheartened child psychologist.

Name: Man of Steel
Text ShortCut: An alien child is evacuated from his dying world and sent to Earth to live among humans. His peace is threatened when other survivors of his home planet invade Earth.

Name: Ice Age 2: The Meltdown
Text ShortCut: Manny, Sid, and Diego discover that the ice age is coming to an end, and join everybody for a journey to higher ground. On the trip, they discover that Manny, in fact, is not the last of the woolly mammoths.

Name: Kung Fu Panda 2
Generes: Action, Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy
Text ShortCut: Po and his friends fight to stop a peacock villain from conquering China with a deadly new weapon, but first the Dragon Warrior must come to terms with his past.

Name: Justice League
Text ShortCut: Fueled by his restored faith in humanity and inspired by Superman's selfless act, Bruce Wayne enlists the help of his new-found ally, Diana Prince, to face an even greater enemy.

Name: Big Hero 6
Generes: Action, Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: A special bond develops between plus-sized inflatable robot Baymax and prodigy Hiro Hamada, who together team up with a group of friends to form a band of high-tech heroes.

Name: Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald
Text ShortCut: The second installment of the "Fantastic Beasts" series featuring the adventures of Magizoologist Newt Scamander.

Name: Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl
Text ShortCut: Blacksmith Will Turner teams up with eccentric pirate "Captain" Jack Sparrow to save his love, the governor's daughter, from Jack's former pirate allies, who are now undead.

Name: Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones

Name: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 2

Name: Thor: The Dark World

Name: Moana

Text ShortCut: In Ancient Polynesia, when a terrible curse incurred by the Demigod Maui reaches Moana's island, she answers the Ocean's call to seek out the Demigod to set things right.

Name: Sing

Text ShortCut: While trying to lead a quiet suburban life, a family of undercover superheroes are forced into action to save the world.

Name: The Martian

Name: Mamma Mia!

Name: Men in Black
Text ShortCut: A police officer joins a secret organization that polices and monitors extraterrestrial interactions on Earth.

Name: Bruce Almighty

Name: Rio

Name: Wreck-It Ralph

Name: The Hangover

Text ShortCut: When a beautiful stranger leads computer hacker Neo to a forbidding underworld, he discovers the shocking truth--the life he knows is the elaborate deception of an evil cyber-intelligence.

Name: Gladiator
Text ShortCut: A former Roman General sets out to exact vengeance against the corrupt emperor who murdered his family and sent him into slavery.

Name: Pretty Woman
Text ShortCut: A man in a legal but hurtful business needs an escort for some social events, and hires a beautiful prostitute he meets... only to fall in love.

Name: X-Men: The Last Stand

Text ShortCut: Benjamin Gates must follow a clue left in John Wilkes Booth's diary to prove his ancestor's innocence in the assassination of Abraham Lincoln.

Name: Lucy
Text ShortCut: A woman, accidentally caught in a dark deal, turns the tables on her captors and transforms into a merciless warrior evolved beyond human logic.

Name: Mission: Impossible
Text ShortCut: An American agent, under false suspicion of disloyalty, must discover and expose the real spy without the help of his organization.
King Leonidas of Sparta and a force of 300 men fight the Persians at Thermopylae in 480 B.C.

Name: The Last Samurai
Text ShortCut: An American military advisor embraces the Samurai culture he was hired to destroy after he is captured in battle.

Name: Ocean's Eleven

Name: Thor

Name: La La Land

Name: Tarzan
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Drama, Family, Music
Text ShortCut: A man raised by gorillas must decide where he really belongs when he discovers he is a human.

Name: Men in Black II
Text ShortCut: Agent Jay is sent to find Agent Kay and restore his memory after the re-appearance of a case from Kay's past.

Name: The Bourne Ultimatum

Name: Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Squeakquel

Name: Les Misérables

Name: The Exorcist

Name: Terminator 3: Rise of the Machines

Name: Pokémon Detective Pikachu

Name: Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings

Name: The Secret Life of Pets 2

Along the way they encounter dragons, dwarves, merfolk, and a band of lost warriors before reaching the edge of the world.

Name: Jason Bourne
Text ShortCut: The CIA's most dangerous former operative is drawn out of hiding to uncover more explosive truths about his past.

Name: The Wolverine
Text ShortCut: Wolverine comes to Japan to meet an old friend whose life he saved years ago, and gets embroiled in a conspiracy involving yakuza and mutants.

Name: Kingsman: The Secret Service
Text ShortCut: A spy organisation recruits a promising street kid into the agency's training program, while a global threat emerges from a twisted tech genius.

Name: Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian
Text ShortCut: Security guard Larry Daley infiltrates the Smithsonian Institution in order to rescue Jedediah and Octavius, who have been shipped to the museum by mistake.

Name: Batman
Text ShortCut: The Dark Knight of Gotham City begins his war on crime with his first major enemy being Jack Napier, a criminal who becomes the clownishly homicidal Joker.

Name: The Bodyguard
Text ShortCut: A former Secret Service agent takes on the job of bodyguard to an R&B singer, whose lifestyle is most unlike a President's.

Name: Pacific Rim
Text ShortCut: As a war between humankind and monstrous sea creatures wages on, a former pilot and a trainee are paired up to drive a seemingly obsolete special weapon in a desperate effort to save the world from the apocalypse.

Name: Kingsman: The Golden Circle
Text ShortCut: After the Kingsman's headquarters are destroyed and the world is held hostage, an allied spy organisation in the United States is discovered. These two elite secret organisations must band together to defeat a common enemy.

Name: Sing 2
Text ShortCut: Buster Moon and his friends must persuade reclusive rock star Clay Calloway to join them for the opening of a new show.

Name: The Mummy
Text ShortCut: An ancient Egyptian princess is awakened from her crypt beneath the desert, bringing with her malevolence grown over millennia, and terrors that defy human comprehension.

Name: Ice Age 5: Collision Course
Text ShortCut: When Scrat's acorn sends an asteroid to Earth, the Herd must find a way to stop the asteroid from hitting Earth with the help of a returning friend.

Name: Twilight
Text ShortCut: When Bella Swan moves to a small town in the Pacific Northwest, she falls in love with Edward Cullen, a mysterious classmate who reveals himself to be a 108-year-old vampire.

Name: Signs
Text ShortCut: A widowed former reverend living with his children and brother on a Pennsylvania farm finds mysterious crop circles in their fields, which suggests something more frightening to come.

Name: X2: X-Men United
Text ShortCut: When anti-mutant Colonel William Stryker kidnaps Professor X and attacks his school, the X-Men must ally with their archenemy Magneto to stop him.

Name: Alita: Battle Angel
Text ShortCut: A deactivated cyborg's revived, but can't remember anything of her past and goes on a quest to find out who she is.

Name: The Mummy: Tomb of the Dragon Emperor
Text ShortCut: In the Far East, Alex O'Connell, the son of famed mummy fighters Rick and Evy O'Connell, unearths the mummy of the first Emperor of Qin -- a shape-shifting entity cursed by a witch centuries ago.

Name: Prometheus
Text ShortCut: Following clues to the origin of mankind, a team finds a structure on a distant moon, but they soon realize they are not alone.

Name: Gone with the Wind
Text ShortCut: The manipulative daughter of a Georgia plantation owner conducts a turbulent romance with a roguish profiteer during the American Civil War and Reconstruction periods.

Name: Mamma Mia! Here We Go Again
Text ShortCut: Five years after the events of Mamma Mia!, Sophie prepares for the grand reopening of the Hotel Bella Donna as she learns more about her mother's past.

Name: Eternals
Text ShortCut: The saga of the Eternals, a race of immortal beings who lived on Earth and shaped its history and civilizations.

Name: Uncharted
Text ShortCut: Street-smart Nathan Drake is recruited by seasoned treasure hunter Victor "Sully" Sullivan to recover a fortune amassed by Ferdinand Magellan, and lost 500 years ago by the House of Moncada.

Name: Dune
Text ShortCut: A noble family becomes embroiled in a war for control over the galaxy's most valuable asset while its heir becomes troubled by visions of a dark future.

Name: TRON: Legacy
Text ShortCut: The son of a virtual world designer goes looking for his father and ends up inside the digital world that his father designed. He meets his father's corrupted creation and a unique ally who was born inside the digital world.

Name: Mission: Impossible III
Text ShortCut: IMF agent Ethan Hunt comes into conflict with a dangerous and sadistic arms dealer who threatens his life and his fiancée in response.

Name: Snow White and the Huntsman
Text ShortCut: In a twist to the fairy tale, the Huntsman ordered to take Snow White into the woods to be killed winds up becoming her protector and mentor in a quest to vanquish the Evil Queen.

Name: Grease
Text ShortCut: Good girl Sandy Olsson and greaser Danny Zuko fell in love over the summer. When they unexpectedly discover they're now in the same high school, will they be able to rekindle their romance?

Name: Toy Story
Text ShortCut: A cowboy doll is profoundly threatened and jealous when a new spaceman figure supplants him as top toy in a boy's room.

Name: Solo: A Star Wars Story
Text ShortCut: Board the Millennium Falcon and journey to a galaxy far, far away in an epic action-adventure that will set the course of one of the Star Wars saga's most unlikely heroes.

Name: The Wolf of Wall Street
Text ShortCut: Based on the true story of Jordan Belfort, from his rise to a wealthy stock-broker living the high life to his fall involving crime, corruption and the federal government.

Name: Superman Returns
Text ShortCut: Superman returns to Earth after spending five years in space examining his homeworld Krypton. But he finds things have changed while he was gone, and he must once again prove himself important to the world.

Name: Robin Hood: Prince of Thieves
Text ShortCut: Robin Hood decides to fight back as an outlaw when faced with the tyranny of the Sheriff of Nottingham.

Name: Indiana Jones and the Raiders of the Lost Ark
Text ShortCut: In 1936, archaeologist and adventurer Indiana Jones is hired by the U.S. government to find the Ark of the Covenant before Adolf Hitler's Nazis can obtain its awesome powers.

Name: Independence Day: Resurgence
Text ShortCut: Two decades after the first Independence Day invasion, Earth is faced with a new extra-Solar threat. But will mankind's new space defenses be enough?

Name: Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore
Text ShortCut: Albus Dumbledore assigns Newt and his allies with a mission related to the rising power of Grindelwald.

Name: Live Free or Die Hard
Text ShortCut: John McClane and a young hacker join forces to take down master cyber-terrorist Thomas Gabriel in Washington D.C.

Name: Monster Hunt
Text ShortCut: Human and monsters have lived in their separate worlds, but after the birth of Wuba, the last of the monster kings, begins the adventure to bring the two races together.

Name: Godzilla: King of the Monsters
Text ShortCut: The crypto-zoological agency Monarch faces off against a battery of god-sized monsters, including the mighty Godzilla, who collides with Mothra, Rodan, and his ultimate nemesis, the three-headed King Ghidorah.

Name: Home
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: An alien on the run from his own people makes friends with a girl. He tries to help her on her quest, but can be an interference.

Name: Star Trek
Text ShortCut: The brash James T. Kirk tries to live up to his father's legacy with Mr. Spock keeping him in check as a vengeful Romulan from the future creates black holes to destroy the Federation one planet at a time.

April 6th, 1917. As an infantry battalion assembles to wage war deep in enemy territory, two soldiers are assigned to race against time and deliver a message that will stop 1,600 men from walking straight into a deadly trap.

Name: Happy Feet
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Music, Musical, Romance
Text ShortCut: Into the world of the Emperor Penguins, who find their soul mates through song, a penguin is born who cannot sing. But he can tap dance something fierce!

Name: Cars 3
Text ShortCut: Lightning McQueen sets out to prove to a new generation of racers that he's still the best race car in the world.

Name: Back to the Future
Text ShortCut: Marty McFly, a 17-year-old high school student, is accidentally sent thirty years into the past in a time-traveling DeLorean invented by his close friend, the eccentric scientist Doc Brown.

Name: Ice Age
Text ShortCut: The story revolves around sub-zero heroes: a woolly mammoth, a saber-toothed tiger, a sloth and a prehistoric combination of a squirrel and rat, known as Scrat.

Name: Fifty Shades Darker
Text ShortCut: While Christian wrestles with his inner demons, Anastasia must confront the anger and envy of the women who came before her.

Name: Monsters vs. Aliens
Generes: Action, Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: A woman transformed into a giant after she is struck by a meteorite on her wedding day becomes part of a team of monsters sent in by the U.S. government to defeat an alien mastermind trying to take over Earth.

Name: Black Widow
Text ShortCut: Natasha Romanoff confronts the darker parts of her ledger when a dangerous conspiracy with ties to her past arises.

Name: Godzilla
Text ShortCut: French nuclear tests irradiate an iguana into a giant monster that heads off to New York City. The American military must chase the monster across the city to stop it before it reproduces.

Name: True Lies
Text ShortCut: A fearless, globe-trotting, terrorist-battling secret agent has his life turned upside down when he discovers his wife might be having an affair with a used-car salesman while terrorists smuggle nuclear war heads into the United States.

Name: Slumdog Millionaire
Text ShortCut: A Mumbai teenager reflects on his life after being accused of cheating on the Indian version of "Who Wants to be a Millionaire?".

Name: Sonic the Hedgehog 2
Generes: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: When the manic Dr Robotnik returns to Earth with a new ally, Knuckles the Echidna, Sonic and his new friend Tails is all that stands in their way.

Name: Taken 2
Text ShortCut: In Istanbul, retired CIA operative Bryan Mills and his wife are taken hostage by the father of a kidnapper Mills killed while rescuing his daughter.

Name: G.I. Joe: Retaliation
Text ShortCut: The G.I. Joes are not only fighting their mortal enemy Cobra; they are forced to contend with threats from within the government that jeopardize their very existence.

Name: Mad Max: Fury Road
Text ShortCut: In a post-apocalyptic wasteland, a woman rebels against a tyrannical ruler in search for her homeland with the aid of a group of female prisoners, a psychotic worshiper, and a drifter named Max.

Name: Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse
Generes: Action, Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: Teen Miles Morales becomes the Spider-Man of his universe, and must join with five spider-powered individuals from other dimensions to stop a threat for all realities.

Name: Shark Tale
Text ShortCut: When a son of a gangster shark boss is accidentally killed while on the hunt, his would-be prey and his vegetarian brother decide to use the incident to their own advantage.

Name: Once Upon a Time... In Hollywood
Text ShortCut: A faded television actor and his stunt double strive to achieve fame and success in the final years of Hollywood's Golden Age in 1969 Los Angeles.

Name: What Women Want
Text ShortCut: A cocky, chauvinistic advertising executive magically acquires the ability to hear what women are thinking.

Name: The Adventures of Tintin
Text ShortCut: Intrepid reporter Tintin and Captain Haddock set off on a treasure hunt for a sunken ship commanded by Haddock's ancestor.

Name: Batman Begins
Text ShortCut: After training with his mentor, Batman begins his fight to free crime-ridden Gotham City from corruption.

Name: Penguins of Madagascar
Text ShortCut: Skipper, Kowalski, Rico and Private join forces with undercover organization The North Wind to stop the villainous Dr. Octavius Brine from destroying the world as we know it.

Name: X-Men Origins: Wolverine
Text ShortCut: The early years of James Logan, featuring his rivalry with his brother Victor Creed, his service in the special forces team Weapon X, and his experimentation into the metal-lined mutant Wolverine.

Name: The Golden Compass
Text ShortCut: In a parallel universe, young Lyra Belacqua journeys to the far North to save her best friend and other kidnapped children from terrible experiments by a mysterious organization.

Name: Fifty Shades Freed
Text ShortCut: Anastasia and Christian get married, but Jack Hyde continues to threaten their relationship.

Name: Hitch
Text ShortCut: A smooth-talking man falls for a hardened columnist while helping a shy accountant woo a beautiful heiress.

Name: Terminator Salvation
Text ShortCut: In 2018, a mysterious new weapon in the war against the machines, half-human and half-machine, comes to John Connor on the eve of a resistance attack on Skynet. But whose side is he on, and can he be trusted?

Name: Captain America: The First Avenger
Text ShortCut: Steve Rogers, a rejected military soldier, transforms into Captain America after taking a dose of a "Super-Soldier serum". But being Captain America comes at a price as he attempts to take down a warmonger and a terrorist organization.

Name: Edge of Tomorrow
Text ShortCut: A soldier fighting aliens gets to relive the same day over and over again, the day restarting every time he dies.

Name: There's Something About Mary
Text ShortCut: A man gets a chance to meet up with his dream girl from high school, even though his date with her back then was a complete disaster.

Name: Gone Girl
Text ShortCut: With his wife's disappearance having become the focus of an intense media circus, a man sees the spotlight turned on him when it's suspected that he may not be innocent.

Name: The Fugitive
Text ShortCut: Dr. Richard Kimble, unjustly accused of murdering his wife, must find the real killer while being the target of a nationwide manhunt led by a seasoned U.S. Marshal.

Name: Jurassic Park III
Text ShortCut: A decidedly odd couple with ulterior motives convince Dr. Grant to go to Isla Sorna for a holiday, but their unexpected landing startles the island's new inhabitants.

Name: My Big Fat Greek Wedding
Text ShortCut: A young Greek woman falls in love with a non-Greek and struggles to get her family to accept him while she comes to terms with her heritage and cultural identity.

Name: Hello Mr. Billionaire
Text ShortCut: A pathetic minor league Soccer Goalkeeper was given a task - to spend 1 Billion in thirty days, if successful he will get 30 Billion. However, he's not allowed to tell anyone about the task and he must not own any valuables by end of it.

Name: Die Hard with a Vengeance
Text ShortCut: John McClane and a Harlem store owner are targeted by German terrorist Simon in New York City, where he plans to rob the Federal Reserve Building.

Name: Shazam!
Text ShortCut: A newly fostered young boy in search of his mother instead finds unexpected super powers and soon gains a powerful enemy.

Name: The Nun
Text ShortCut: A priest with a haunted past and a novice on the threshold of her final vows are sent by the Vatican to investigate the death of a young nun in Romania and confront a malevolent force in the form of a demonic nun.

Name: Alvin and the Chipmunks
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Drama, Family, Fantasy, Music, Musical
Text ShortCut: Three musical chipmunks are discovered by an aspiring songwriter who wants to use their amazing singing abilities to become famous.

Name: Notting Hill
Text ShortCut: The life of a simple bookshop owner changes when he meets the most famous film star in the world.

Name: Tenet
Text ShortCut: Armed with only one word, Tenet, and fighting for the survival of the entire world, a Protagonist journeys through a twilight world of international espionage on a mission that will unfold in something beyond real time.

Name: A Bug's Life
Text ShortCut: A misfit ant, looking for "warriors" to save his colony from greedy grasshoppers, recruits a group of bugs that turn out to be an inept circus troupe.

Name: Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb
Text ShortCut: Larry spans the globe, uniting favorite and new characters while embarking on an epic quest to save the magic before it is gone forever.

Name: Ocean's Twelve
Text ShortCut: Daniel Ocean recruits one more team member so he can pull off three major European heists in this sequel to Ocean's Eleven.

Name: Planet of the Apes
Text ShortCut: In 2029, an Air Force astronaut crash-lands on a mysterious planet where evolved, talking apes dominate a race of primitive humans.

Name: The Hangover Part III
Text ShortCut: When one of their own is kidnapped by an angry gangster, the Wolf Pack must track down Mr. Chow, who has escaped from prison and is on the run.

Name: The World Is Not Enough
Text ShortCut: James Bond uncovers a nuclear plot while protecting an oil heiress from her former kidnapper, an international terrorist who can't feel pain.

Name: Monster Hunt 2
Text ShortCut: The story continues with Wuba after he parts way with his human parents Tian and Lan for his own journey. Peace has not been restored in the monster world after the death of the evil monster king.

Name: Fast & Furious
Text ShortCut: Brian O'Conner, back working for the FBI in Los Angeles, teams up with Dominic Toretto to bring down a heroin importer by infiltrating his operation.

Name: Noah
Text ShortCut: Noah is chosen by God to undertake a momentous mission before an apocalyptic flood cleanses the world.

Name: The Karate Kid
Text ShortCut: Work causes a single mother to move to China with her young son; in his new home, the boy embraces kung fu, taught to him by a master.

Name: Home Alone 2: Lost in New York
Text ShortCut: One year after Kevin McCallister was left home alone and had to defeat a pair of bumbling burglars, he accidentally finds himself stranded in New York City - and the same criminals are not far behind.

Name: Hotel Transylvania
Text ShortCut: Dracula, who operates a high-end resort away from the human world, goes into overprotective mode when a boy discovers the resort and falls for the count's teenaged daughter.

Name: Minority Report
Text ShortCut: In a future where a special police unit is able to arrest murderers before they commit their crimes, an officer from that unit is himself accused of a future murder.

Name: Your Name.
Text ShortCut: Two strangers find themselves linked in a bizarre way. When a connection forms, will distance be the only thing to keep them apart?

Name: Top Gun
Text ShortCut: As students at the United States Navy's elite fighter weapons school compete to be best in the class, one daring young pilot learns a few things from a civilian instructor that are not taught in the classroom.

Name: The Legend of Tarzan
Text ShortCut: Tarzan, having acclimated to life in London, is called back to his former home in the jungle to investigate the activities at a mining encampment.

Name: American Beauty
Text ShortCut: A sexually frustrated suburban father has a mid-life crisis after becoming infatuated with his daughter's best friend.

Name: Spirited Away
Text ShortCut: During her family's move to the suburbs, a sullen 10-year-old girl wanders into a world ruled by gods, witches, and spirits, and where humans are changed into beasts.

Name: Apollo 13
Text ShortCut: NASA must devise a strategy to return Apollo 13 to Earth safely after the spacecraft undergoes massive internal damage putting the lives of the three astronauts on board in jeopardy.

Name: Rain Man
Text ShortCut: After a selfish L.A. yuppie learns his estranged father left a fortune to an autistic-savant brother in Ohio that he didn't know existed, he absconds with his brother and sets out across the country, hoping to gain a larger inheritance.

Name: The Great Gatsby
Text ShortCut: A writer and wall street trader, Nick, finds himself drawn to the past and lifestyle of his millionaire neighbor, Jay Gatsby.

Name: Dumbo
Text ShortCut: A young elephant, whose oversized ears enable him to fly, helps save a struggling circus, but when the circus plans a new venture, Dumbo and his friends discover dark secrets beneath its shiny veneer.

Name: I, Robot
Text ShortCut: In 2035, a technophobic cop investigates a crime that may have been perpetrated by a robot, which leads to a larger threat to humanity.

Name: Basic Instinct
Text ShortCut: A violent police detective investigates a brutal murder that might involve a manipulative and seductive novelist.

Name: Murder on the Orient Express
Text ShortCut: When a murder occurs on the train on which he's travelling, celebrated detective Hercule Poirot is recruited to solve the case.

Name: X-Men: First Class
Text ShortCut: In the 1960s, superpowered humans Charles Xavier and Erik Lensherr work together to find others like them, but Erik's vengeful pursuit of an ambitious mutant who ruined his life causes a schism to divide them.

Name: The Angry Birds Movie
Text ShortCut: When an island populated by happy, flightless birds is visited by mysterious green piggies, it's up to three unlikely outcasts - Red, Chuck and Bomb - to figure out what the pigs are up to.

Name: GoldenEye
Text ShortCut: Years after a friend and fellow 00 agent is killed on a joint mission, a Russian crime syndicate steals a secret space-based weapons program known as "GoldenEye" and James Bond has to stop them from using it.

Name: Catch Me If You Can
Text ShortCut: Barely 21 yet, Frank is a skilled forger who has passed as a doctor, lawyer and pilot. FBI agent Carl becomes obsessed with tracking down the con man, who only revels in the pursuit.

Name: Now You See Me
Text ShortCut: An F.B.I. Agent and an Interpol Detective track a team of illusionists who pull off bank heists during their performances, and reward their audiences with the money.

Name: Hannibal
Text ShortCut: Living in exile, Dr. Hannibal Lecter tries to reconnect with now disgraced F.B.I. Agent Clarice Starling, and finds himself a target for revenge from a powerful victim.

Name: The Mask
Text ShortCut: Bank clerk Stanley Ipkiss is transformed into a manic superhero when he wears a mysterious mask.

Name: Peter Rabbit
Generes: Adventure, Comedy, Crime, Drama, Family, Fantasy
Text ShortCut: Feature adaptation of Beatrix Potter's classic tale of a rebellious rabbit trying to sneak into a farmer's vegetable garden.

Name: Speed
Text ShortCut: A young police officer must prevent a bomb exploding aboard a city bus by keeping its speed above 50 mph.

Name: Dinosaur
Text ShortCut: An orphaned dinosaur raised by lemurs joins an arduous trek to a sanctuary after a meteorite shower destroys his family home.

Name: Mary Poppins Returns
Text ShortCut: A few decades after her original visit, Mary Poppins, the magical nanny, returns to help the Banks siblings and Michael's children through a difficult time in their lives.

Name: Deep Impact
Text ShortCut: A comet is discovered to be on a collision course with Earth. As doomsday nears, the human race prepares for the worst.

Name: The Lorax
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Drama, Family, Fantasy, Musical
Text ShortCut: A 12-year-old boy searches for the one thing that will enable him to win the affection of the girl of his dreams. To find it he must discover the story of the Lorax, the grumpy yet charming creature who fights to protect his world.

Name: The Maze Runner
Text ShortCut: Thomas is deposited in a community of boys after his memory is erased, soon learning they're all trapped in a maze that will require him to join forces with fellow "runners" for a shot at escape.

Name: The Smurfs 2
Text ShortCut: The Smurfs team up with their human friends to rescue Smurfette, who has been abducted by Gargamel, since she knows a secret spell that can turn the evil sorcerer's newest creation, creatures called "The Naughties", into real Smurfs.

Name: National Treasure
Text ShortCut: A historian races to find the legendary Templar Treasure before a team of mercenaries.

Name: Rush Hour 2
Text ShortCut: Carter and Lee head to Hong Kong for a vacation, but become embroiled in a counterfeit money scam.

Name: Trolls
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Musical, Romance
Text ShortCut: After the Bergens invade Troll Village, Poppy, the happiest Troll ever born, and the curmudgeonly Branch set off on a journey to rescue her friends.

Name: xXx: Return of Xander Cage
Text ShortCut: Xander Cage is left for dead after an incident, though he secretly returns to action for a new, tough assignment with his handler Augustus Gibbons.

Name: Pocahontas
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Drama, Family, Musical, Romance
Text ShortCut: An English soldier and the daughter of an Algonquin chief share a romance when English colonists invade seventeenth century Virginia.

Name: How the Grinch Stole Christmas
Text ShortCut: On the outskirts of Whoville lives a green, revenge-seeking Grinch who plans to ruin Christmas for all of the citizens of the town.

Name: Star Trek Beyond
Text ShortCut: The crew of the USS Enterprise explores the furthest reaches of uncharted space, where they encounter a new ruthless enemy, who puts them, and everything the Federation stands for, to the test.

Name: Alvin and the Chipmunks: Chipwrecked
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Music, Musical
Text ShortCut: Playing around while aboard a cruise ship, the Chipmunks and Chipettes accidentally go overboard and end up marooned in a tropical paradise. They discover their new turf is not as deserted as it seems.

Name: Wanted
Text ShortCut: A frustrated office worker discovers that he is the son of a professional assassin, and that he shares his father's superhuman killing abilities.

Name: The Flintstones
Text ShortCut: In a parallel modern-day Stone Age world, a working-class family, the Flintstones, are set up for an executive job. But they learn that money can't buy happiness.

Name: A Quiet Place
Text ShortCut: In a post-apocalyptic world, a family is forced to live in silence while hiding from monsters with ultra-sensitive hearing.

Name: Enchanted
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Musical, Romance
Text ShortCut: A young maiden in a land called Andalasia, who is prepared to be wed, is sent away to New York City by an evil Queen, where she falls in love with a lawyer.

Name: Over the Hedge
Text ShortCut: A scheming raccoon fools a mismatched family of forest creatures into helping him repay a debt of food, by invading the new suburban sprawl that popped up while they were hibernating...and learns a lesson about family himself.

Name: 300: Rise of an Empire
Text ShortCut: Greek general Themistocles of Athens leads the naval charge against invading Persian forces led by mortal-turned-god Xerxes and Artemisia, vengeful commander of the Persian navy.

Name: Batman Forever
Text ShortCut: Batman must battle former district attorney Harvey Dent, who is now Two-Face and Edward Nygma, The Riddler with help from an amorous psychologist and a young circus acrobat who becomes his sidekick, Robin.

Name: Prince of Persia: The Sands of Time
Text ShortCut: A young fugitive prince and princess must stop a villain who unknowingly threatens to destroy the world with a special dagger that enables the magic sand inside to reverse time.

Name: The Curious Case of Benjamin Button
Text ShortCut: Tells the story of Benjamin Button, a man who starts aging backwards with consequences.

Name: Journey 2: The Mysterious Island
Generes: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: Sean Anderson partners with his mom's husband on a mission to find his grandfather, who is thought to be missing on a mythical island.

Name: The Rock
Text ShortCut: A mild-mannered chemist and an ex-con must lead the counterstrike when a rogue group of military men, led by a renegade general, threaten a nerve gas attack from Alcatraz against San Francisco.

Name: The Great Wall
Text ShortCut: In ancient China, a group of European mercenaries encounters a secret army that maintains and defends the Great Wall of China against a horde of monstrous creatures.

Name: Now You See Me 2
Generes: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Crime, Mystery, Thriller
Text ShortCut: The Four Horsemen resurface, and are forcibly recruited by a tech genius to pull off their most impossible heist yet.

Name: Never Say Die
Text ShortCut: A male UFC boxer switches bodies with the female reporter who exposed his bribes. Now they must help each other win the championship.

Name: Fantastic Four
Text ShortCut: A group of astronauts gain superpowers after a cosmic radiation exposure and must use them to oppose the plans of their enemy, Doctor Victor Von Doom.

Name: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom
Text ShortCut: In 1935, Indiana Jones arrives in India, still part of the British Empire, and is asked to find a mystical stone. He then stumbles upon a secret cult committing enslavement and human sacrifices in the catacombs of an ancient palace.

Name: Tomorrow Never Dies
Text ShortCut: James Bond sets out to stop a media mogul's plan to induce war between China and the UK in order to obtain exclusive global media coverage.

Name: Back to the Future Part II
Text ShortCut: After visiting 2015, Marty McFly must repeat his visit to 1955 to prevent disastrous changes to 1985...without interfering with his first trip.

Name: The Good Dinosaur
Text ShortCut: In a world where dinosaurs and humans live side-by-side, an Apatosaurus named Arlo makes an unlikely human friend.

Name: Free Guy
Text ShortCut: A bank teller discovers that he's actually an NPC inside a brutal, open world video game.

Name: 22 Jump Street
Text ShortCut: After making their way through high school (twice), big changes are in store for officers Schmidt and Jenko when they go deep undercover at a local college.

Name: Meet the Parents
Text ShortCut: Male nurse Greg Focker meets his girlfriend's parents before proposing, but her suspicious father is every date's worst nightmare.

Name: Who Framed Roger Rabbit
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Crime, Family, Fantasy, Mystery
Text ShortCut: A toon-hating detective is a cartoon rabbit's only hope to prove his innocence when he is accused of murder.

Name: Black Swan
Text ShortCut: A committed dancer struggles to maintain her sanity after winning the lead role in a production of Tchaikovsky's "Swan Lake".

Name: The Perfect Storm
Text ShortCut: An unusually intense storm pattern catches some commercial fishermen unaware and puts them in mortal danger.

Name: Crocodile Dundee
Text ShortCut: An American reporter goes to the Australian outback to meet an eccentric crocodile poacher and invites him to New York City.

Name: Crazy Alien
Text ShortCut: A monkey trainer whose act goes wrong after an alien crash lands on Earth and injures his monkey. Desperate to perform the act, he attempts to train the alien instead, but is punished after the alien regains his powers.

Name: Se7en
Text ShortCut: Two detectives, a rookie and a veteran, hunt a serial killer who uses the seven deadly sins as his motives.

Name: John Wick: Chapter 3 - Parabellum
Text ShortCut: John Wick is on the run after killing a member of the international assassins' guild, and with a $14 million price tag on his head, he is the target of hit men and women everywhere.

Name: The Devil Wears Prada
Text ShortCut: A smart but sensible new graduate lands a job as an assistant to Miranda Priestly, the demanding editor-in-chief of a high fashion magazine.

Name: Taken 3
Text ShortCut: Accused of a ruthless murder he never committed or witnessed, Bryan Mills goes on the run and brings out his particular set of skills to find the true killer and clear his name.

Name: The Hunchback of Notre Dame
Text ShortCut: A deformed bell-ringer must assert his independence from a vicious government minister in order to help his friend, a gypsy dancer.

Name: A Christmas Carol
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Drama, Family, Fantasy
Text ShortCut: An animated retelling of Charles Dickens' classic novel about a Victorian-era miser taken on a journey of self-redemption, courtesy of several mysterious Christmas apparitions.

Name: The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water
Text ShortCut: When a diabolical pirate above the sea steals the secret Krabby Patty formula, SpongeBob and his nemesis Plankton must team up in order to get it back.

Name: Schindler's List
Text ShortCut: In German-occupied Poland during World War II, industrialist Oskar Schindler gradually becomes concerned for his Jewish workforce after witnessing their persecution by the Nazis.

Name: Megamind
Generes: Action, Animation, Comedy, Crime, Family, Mystery, Sci-Fi, Thriller
Text ShortCut: Evil genius Megamind finally defeats his do-gooder nemesis, Metro Man, but is left without a purpose in a superhero-free world.

Name: The Conjuring 2
Text ShortCut: Ed and Lorraine Warren travel to North London to help a single mother raising four children alone in a house plagued by a supernatural spirit.

Name: Green Book
Text ShortCut: A working-class Italian-American bouncer becomes the driver of an African-American classical pianist on a tour of venues through the 1960s American South.

Name: Lethal Weapon 3
Text ShortCut: Martin Riggs and Roger Murtaugh pursue a former LAPD officer who uses his knowledge of police procedure and policies to steal and sell confiscated guns and ammunition to local street gangs.

Name: The Ugly Truth
Text ShortCut: An uptight television producer takes control of a morning show segment on modern relationships hosted by a misogynistic man.

Name: Robin Hood
Text ShortCut: In twelfth-century England, Robin Longstride and his band of marauders confront corruption in a local village and lead an uprising against the crown that will forever alter the balance of world power.

Name: Inglourious Basterds
Text ShortCut: In Nazi-occupied France during World War II, a plan to assassinate Nazi leaders by a group of Jewish U.S. soldiers coincides with a theatre owner's vengeful plans for the same.

Name: 101 Dalmatians
Text ShortCut: An evil high-fashion designer plots to steal dalmatian puppies in order to make an extravagant fur coat but creates an extravagant mess instead.

Name: The Conjuring
Text ShortCut: Paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren work to help a family terrorized by a dark presence in their farmhouse.

Name: Fatal Attraction
Text ShortCut: A married man's one-night stand comes back to haunt him when that lover begins to stalk him and his family.

Name: Sonic the Hedgehog
Generes: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: After discovering a small, blue, fast hedgehog, a small-town police officer must help him defeat an evil genius who wants to do experiments on him.

Name: The Last Airbender
Text ShortCut: Follows the adventures of Aang, a young successor to a long line of Avatars, who must master all four elements and stop the Fire Nation from enslaving the Water Tribes and the Earth Kingdom.

Name: The Proposal
Text ShortCut: A pushy boss forces her young assistant to marry her in order to keep her visa status in the U.S. and avoid deportation to Canada.

Name: A Beautiful Mind
Text ShortCut: After John Nash, a brilliant but asocial mathematician, accepts secret work in cryptography, his life takes a turn for the nightmarish.

Name: Beverly Hills Cop
Text ShortCut: A freewheeling Detroit cop pursuing a murder investigation finds himself dealing with the very different culture of Beverly Hills.

Name: The Polar Express
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Musical
Text ShortCut: On Christmas Eve, a young boy embarks on a magical adventure to the North Pole on the Polar Express, while learning about friendship, bravery, and the spirit of Christmas.

Name: Air Force One
Text ShortCut: Communist radicals hijack Air Force One with the U.S. President and his family on board. The Vice President negotiates from Washington D.C., while the President, a veteran, fights to rescue the hostages on board.

Name: The Expendables 2
Text ShortCut: Mr. Church reunites the Expendables for what should be an easy paycheck, but when one of their men is murdered on the job, their quest for revenge puts them deep in enemy territory and up against an unexpected threat.

Name: Chicken Little
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: After ruining his reputation with the town, a courageous chicken must come to the rescue of his fellow citizens when aliens start an invasion.

Name: As Good as It Gets
Text ShortCut: A single mother and waitress, a misanthropic author, and a gay artist form an unlikely friendship after the artist is assaulted in a robbery.

Name: Maze Runner: The Scorch Trials
Text ShortCut: After having escaped the Maze, the Gladers now face a new set of challenges on the open roads of a desolate landscape filled with unimaginable obstacles.

Name: Resident Evil: The Final Chapter
Text ShortCut: Alice returns to where the nightmare began: The Hive in Raccoon City, where the Umbrella Corporation is gathering its forces for a final strike against the only remaining survivors of the apocalypse.

Name: The Lego Batman Movie
Generes: Action, Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: A cooler-than-ever Bruce Wayne must deal with the usual suspects as they plan to rule Gotham City, while discovering that he has accidentally adopted a teenage orphan who wishes to become his sidekick.

Name: Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me
Text ShortCut: Dr. Evil is back and has invented a new time machine that allows him to go back to the 1960s and steal Austin Powers' mojo, inadvertently leaving him "shagless".

Name: Knives Out
Text ShortCut: A detective investigates the death of the patriarch of an eccentric, combative family.

Name: Ocean's Thirteen
Text ShortCut: Danny Ocean rounds up the boys for a third heist after casino owner Willy Bank double-crosses one of the original eleven, Reuben Tishkoff.

Name: Little Fockers
Text ShortCut: Family-patriarch Jack Byrnes wants to appoint a successor. Does his son-in-law, the male nurse Greg Focker, have what it takes?

Name: Bolt
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Crime, Drama, Family, Sci-Fi
Text ShortCut: The canine star of a fictional sci-fi/action show that believes his powers are real embarks on a cross country trek to save his co-star from a threat he believes is just as real.

Name: Ransom
Text ShortCut: Multi-millionaire Tom Mullen's son is kidnapped, but after initially agreeing to pay the ransom Mullen then decides to use the ransom money as a bounty.

Name: Runaway Bride
Text ShortCut: A reporter is assigned to write a story about a woman who has left a string of fiancés at the altar.

Name: The Blind Side
Text ShortCut: The story of Michael Oher, a homeless and traumatized boy who became an All-American football player and first-round NFL draft pick with the help of a caring woman and her family.

Name: The Ex-File 3: The Return of The Exes
Text ShortCut: A couples relationship is tested by the untimely appearances of their exes!

Name: The Fault in Our Stars
Text ShortCut: Two teenage cancer patients begin a life-affirming journey to visit a reclusive author in Amsterdam.

Name: The Pursuit of Happyness
Text ShortCut: A struggling salesman takes custody of his son as he's poised to begin a life-changing professional career.

Name: Rise of the Guardians
Generes: Action, Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Drama, Family, Fantasy
Text ShortCut: When the evil spirit Pitch launches an assault on Earth, the Immortal Guardians team up to protect the innocence of children all around the world.

Name: Close Encounters of the Third Kind
Text ShortCut: Roy Neary, an Indiana electric lineman, finds his quiet and ordinary daily life turned upside down after a close encounter with a UFO, spurring him to an obsessed cross-country quest for answers as a momentous event approaches.

Name: Chicago
Text ShortCut: Two death-row murderesses develop a fierce rivalry while competing for publicity, celebrity, and a sleazy lawyer's attention.

Name: Annabelle: Creation

Name: Wonder

Name: Skyscraper

Name: A Good Day to Die Hard

Name: Mulan
Generes: Adventure, Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Musical, War
Text ShortCut: To save her father from death in the army, a young maiden secretly goes in his place and becomes one of China's greatest heroines in the process.

Name: Dangal
Text ShortCut: Former wrestler Mahavir Singh Phogat and his two wrestler daughters struggle towards glory at the Commonwealth Games in the face of societal oppression.

Name: Passengers
Text ShortCut: A malfunction in a sleeping pod on a spacecraft traveling to a distant colony planet wakes one passenger 90 years early.

Name: Battleship
Text ShortCut: A fleet of ships is forced to do battle with an armada of unknown origins in order to discover and thwart their destructive goals.

Name: Liar Liar
Text ShortCut: A fast-track lawyer can't lie for 24 hours due to his son's birthday wish after he disappoints his son for the last time.

Name: G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra
Text ShortCut: An elite military unit comprised of special operatives known as G.I. Joe, operating out of The Pit, takes on an evil organization led by a notorious arms dealer.

Name: Wrath of the Titans
Text ShortCut: Perseus braves the treacherous underworld to rescue his father, Zeus, captured by his son, Ares, and brother Hades who unleash the ancient Titans upon the world.

Name: Fantastic 4: Rise of the Silver Surfer
